de.mdelab.comparch

Interface AdaptationStrategy

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Annotation, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AdaptationStrategyImpl

    public interface AdaptationStrategy
extends Annotation
    A representation of the model object 'Adaptation Strategy'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Utility Increase
    • Costs
    • Annotations
    • Assigned Issues
    • Input Parameters
    See Also:
    ComparchPackage.getAdaptationStrategy()
